title: Jean Shepherd - Missing Episodes
description:
Here are five Shep recordings that are missing from the big 8-volume Jean Shepherd collection. Includes the following:

1971 09 08 Crystal Radio WOR Jean Shepherd
1971 12 xx Plants Ham Radio WOR Jean Shepherd
1971 Amateur TV WOR Jean Shepherd
1972 09 13 Drunk Tracking WOR Jean Shepherd
1974 11 20 Laying Wire WOR Jean Shepherd

ENJOY!

(This might also be good for someone not yet familiar with Shep to get a taste before committing to the entire collection.)
